<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no, viewport-fit=cover">
  <title>상권 활성화 지원 시스템</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/chart.js"></script>
  <style>
    * { -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
      background: #fff;
      width: 100vw;
      height: 100dvh;
      overflow: hidden;
      overscroll-behavior: none;
      -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;
    }

    /* ── 전체 앱 래퍼 ── */
    #app {
      width: 100vw;
      height: 100dvh;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    /* ── 로그인 화면 ── */
    #view-login {
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background: linear-gradient(160deg, #4c1d95 0%, #5b21b6 50%, #7c3aed 100%);
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      z-index: 100;
      transition: opacity 0.5s;
    }
    #view-login .login-icon { font-size: 56px; margin-bottom: 16px; }
    #view-login h1 { font-size: 22px; font-weight: 800; color: #fff; text-align: center; line-height: 1.4; margin-bottom: 6px; }
    #view-login p { font-size: 12px; color: #c4b5fd; margin-bottom: 40px; }
    .login-card {
      background: #fff;
      border-radius: 24px;
      padding: 28px 24px;
      width: 80%;
      max-width: 320px;
      text-align: center;
      box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
    }
    .avatar {
      width: 64px; height: 64px;
      background: #ede9fe;
      border-radius: 50%;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      font-size: 24px; font-weight: 800; color: #7c3aed;
      margin: 0 auto 12px;
    }
    .login-card h2 { font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; color: #1f2937; margin-bottom: 4px; }
    .login-card p { font-size: 11px; color: #6b7280; margin-bottom: 20px; }
    .login-btn {
      width: 100%;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #7c3aed, #8b5cf6);
      color: #fff;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 15px;
      padding: 14px;
      border-radius: 14px;
      border: none;
      cursor: pointer;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(124,58,237,0.4);
    }

    /* ── 메인 앱 ── */
    #main-app {
      display: none;
      flex-direction: column;
      width: 100vw;
      height: 100dvh;
    }

    /* ── 헤더 ── */
    .app-header {
      background: #fff;
      padding: 52px 20px 14px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #f3f0ff;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: flex-end;
      flex-shrink: 0;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(124,58,237,0.07);
    }
    .header-badge {
      font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700;
      color: #7c3aed; border: 1px solid #7c3aed;
      padding: 2px 8px; border-radius: 6px;
      display: inline-block; margin-bottom: 4px;
    }
    .app-header h2 { font-size: 20px; font-weight: 800; color: #1f2937; }
    .bell-btn { position: relative; cursor: pointer; padding: 4px; }
    .bell-btn i { font-size: 20px; color: #374151; }
    .badge-dot {
      position: absolute; top: 0; right: 0;
      background: #ef4444; color: #fff;
      font-size: 9px; font-weight: 700;
      padding: 1px 4px; border-radius: 10px;
    }

    /* ── 스크롤 영역 ── */
    .tab-content {
      flex: 1;
      overflow-y: auto;
      -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;
      background: #f5f3ff;
      padding-bottom: 20px;
    }

    /* ── 하단 네비게이션 ── */
    .bottom-nav {
      background: #fff;
      border-top: 1px solid #ede9fe;
      display: flex;
      height: 64px;
      padding-bottom: env(safe-area-inset-bottom);
      flex-shrink: 0;
      z-index: 50;
    }
    .nav-item {
      flex: 1; display: flex; flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      cursor: pointer; color: #9ca3af;
      font-size: 10px; font-weight: 600; gap: 3px;
      transition: color 0.2s;
    }
    .nav-item i { font-size: 18px; }
    .nav-item.active { color: #7c3aed; }

    /* ── 토스트 ── */
    #toast-wrap {
      position: fixed;
      bottom: 80px;
      left: 50%;
      transform: translateX(-50%);
      z-index: 200;
      display: flex; flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center; gap: 6px;
      pointer-events: none;
    }
    .toast-msg {
      background: #4c1d95;
      color: #fff;
      font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      border-radius: 24px;
      white-space: nowrap;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.25);
      animation: toastAnim 2.5s ease forwards;
    }
    @keyframes toastAnim {
      0%   { opacity:0; transform:translateY(10px); }
      12%  { opacity:1; transform:translateY(0); }
      80%  { opacity:1; }
      100% { opacity:0; transform:translateY(-6px); }
    }

    /* ── 카드 공통 ── */
    .card {
      background: #fff;
      border-radius: 20px;
      padding: 18px;
      margin: 12px 14px 0;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(124,58,237,0.08);
    }
    .card-title {
      font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; color: #374151;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px;
    }

    /* ── 진행바 ── */
    .prog-wrap { background: #ede9fe; border-radius: 8px; height: 7px; overflow: hidden; }
    .prog-bar  { height: 100%; border-radius: 8px; background: linear-gradient(90deg,#7c3aed,#8b5cf6); transition: width 0.6s; }
    .prog-bar.orange { background: linear-gradient(90deg,#f97316,#fb923c); }
    .prog-bar.red    { background: linear-gradient(90deg,#ef4444,#f87171); }
    .prog-bar.green  { background: linear-gradient(90deg,#10b981,#34d399); }

    /* ── 배지 ── */
    .badge { display:inline-block; font-size:10px; font-weight:700; padding:2px 8px; border-radius:8px; }
    .badge.green  { background:#d1fae5; color:#065f46; }
    .badge.orange { background:#ffedd5; color:#92400e; }
    .badge.red    { background:#fee2e2; color:#991b1b; }
    .badge.purple { background:#ede9fe; color:#6d28d9; }
    .badge.blue   { background:#dbeafe; color:#1e40af; }

    /* ── 그라디언트 히어로 카드 ── */
    .hero-card {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg,#4c1d95 0%,#7c3aed 100%);
      border-radius: 20px;
      padding: 22px 20px;
      margin: 12px 14px 0;
      color: #fff;
      box-shadow: 0 6px 24px rgba(124,58,237,0.35);
    }
    .hero-card .sub { font-size:11px; color:#c4b5fd; font-weight:600; margin-bottom:4px; }
    .hero-card .score { font-size:42px; font-weight:800; line-height:1; }
    .hero-card .score span { font-size:16px; font-weight:400; color:#c4b5fd; margin-left:4px; }
    .hero-card .trend { font-size:11px; color:#a78bfa; margin-top:6px; }

    /* ── 섹션 뷰 ── */
    .view-section { display:none; }
    .view-section.active { display:block; }

    /* ── GPS 터미널 ── */
    .terminal {
      background: #0f0721;
      border-radius: 14px;
      padding: 12px;
      font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
      font-size: 11px;
      height: 120px;
      overflow-y: auto;
      -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;
    }
    .terminal p { margin-bottom: 4px; line-height: 1.5; }

    /* ── Before/After 슬라이더 ── */
    #slider-container {
      width:100%; height:200px;
      border-radius:14px; overflow:hidden;
      position:relative; background:#ddd;
      touch-action: none;
    }
    #slider-container img { position:absolute; top:0; left:0; width:100%; height:100%; object-fit:cover; }
    #slider-before {
      position:absolute; top:0; left:0; height:100%; overflow:hidden;
      border-right:2px solid #fff; z-index:2; pointer-events:none;
    }
    #slider-before img { position:absolute; top:0; left:0; height:100%; width:350px; object-fit:cover; }
    #slider-range {
      position:absolute; inset:0; opacity:0; cursor:ew-resize; z-index:5;
    }
    .slider-handle {
      position:absolute; top:50%; left:50%; z-index:4; pointer-events:none;
      transform:translate(-50%,-50%);
      background:#fff; border-radius:50%; width:36px; height:36px;
      display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center;
      box-shadow:0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.3); color:#7c3aed; font-size:14px;
    }

    /* ── 바텀시트 ── */
    #bottom-sheet {
      position:fixed; bottom:0; left:0; right:0;
      background:#fff; border-radius:24px 24px 0 0;
      padding:24px 20px 40px;
      z-index:150;
      transform:translateY(100%);
      transition:transform 0.3s ease;
      box-shadow:0 -8px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
    }
    #bottom-sheet.open { transform:translateY(0); }
    #bs-overlay {
      position:fixed; inset:0; background:rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
      z-index:140; display:none;
    }
    #bs-overlay.open { display:block; }

    /* ── 타임라인 ── */
    .timeline-step {
      display:flex; align-items:flex-start; gap:12px;
      margin-bottom:14px; position:relative;
    }
    .step-icon {
      width:28px; height:28px; border-radius:50%;
      display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center;
      font-size:12px; font-weight:700; flex-shrink:0;
      margin-top:2px;
    }
    .step-icon.done   { background:#7c3aed; color:#fff; }
    .step-icon.active { background:#f59e0b; color:#fff; }
    .step-icon.wait   { background:#e5e7eb; color:#9ca3af; }
    .step-line {
      position:absolute; left:13px; top:30px;
      width:2px; height:calc(100% - 4px);
      background:#e5e7eb;
    }
    .step-icon.done ~ .step-line { background:#7c3aed; }

    /* ── 체크박스 투표 ── */
    .vote-item {
      display:flex; align-items:center; gap:12px;
      padding:12px 14px; background:#faf5ff;
      border:2px solid #ede9fe; border-radius:12px;
      margin-bottom:8px; cursor:pointer;
    }
    .vote-item.checked { border-color:#7c3aed; background:#f5f3ff; }
    .vote-check {
      width:22px; height:22px; border-radius:6px;
      border:2px solid #d1d5db;
      display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center;
      font-size:13px; flex-shrink:0; transition:all 0.2s;
    }
    .vote-item.checked .vote-check {
      background:#7c3aed; border-color:#7c3aed; color:#fff;
    }
    .vote-item label { font-size:13px; font-weight:600; color:#374151; cursor:pointer; }

    /* ── 수평 스크롤 카드 ── */
    .hscroll { display:flex; gap:10px; overflow-x:auto; -webkit-overflow-scrolling:touch; padding:4px 0 8px; }
    .hscroll::-webkit-scrollbar { display:none; }
    .h-card {
      min-width:160px; background:#fff; border-radius:16px;
      padding:14px 16px; box-shadow:0 2px 10px rgba(124,58,237,0.1);
      border:1px solid #ede9fe; flex-shrink:0;
    }

    /* ── 테이블 ── */
    .data-row {
      display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center;
      padding:10px 0; border-bottom:1px solid #f3f4f6; gap:8px;
    }
    .data-row:last-child { border-bottom:none; }
    .data-label { font-size:12px; color:#6b7280; flex:1; }
    .data-val   { font-size:12px; font-weight:700; color:#374151; text-align:right; }
    .data-bar-wrap { flex:1; }

    /* ── 토글 스위치 ── */
    .toggle-wrap { position:relative; display:inline-block; width:48px; height:26px; }
    .toggle-wrap input { opacity:0; width:0; height:0; }
    .toggle-slider {
      position:absolute; cursor:pointer;
      top:0; left:0; right:0; bottom:0;
      background:#d1d5db; border-radius:26px;
      transition:0.3s;
    }
    .toggle-slider:before {
      position:absolute; content:"";
      height:20px; width:20px;
      left:3px; bottom:3px;
      background:#fff; border-radius:50%;
      transition:0.3s;
    }
    .toggle-wrap input:checked + .toggle-slider { background:#7c3aed; }
    .toggle-wrap input:checked + .toggle-slider:before { transform:translateX(22px); }

    /* ── 공모 가점 테이블 ── */
    .score-row {
      display:flex; justify-content:space-between;
      padding:10px 14px; border-radius:10px;
      margin-bottom:6px; background:#f5f3ff;
    }
    .score-row .label { font-size:12px; color:#4b5563; }
    .score-row .val   { font-size:13px; font-weight:800; color:#7c3aed; }
    .score-total {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg,#5b21b6,#7c3aed);
      color:#fff; border-radius:14px;
      padding:14px 16px; margin-top:10px;
      display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center;
    }
    .score-total .t-label { font-size:12px; color:#c4b5fd; }
    .score-total .t-val   { font-size:18px; font-weight:800; }

    .no-scroll::-webkit-scrollbar { display:none; }
    .no-scroll { -ms-overflow-style:none; scrollbar-width:none; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
<div id="app">

  <div id="view-login">
    <i class="login-icon" style="font-style: normal;">🏛️</i>
    <h1>공공 예산 연동형<br>상권 활성화 지원 시스템</h1>
    <p>누적 데이터 1,420건 · AI 진단 준비 완료</p>
    <div class="login-card">
      <div class="avatar">홍</div>
      <h2>홍석기 센터장</h2>
      <p>서구청 · 마스터 권한</p>
      <button class="login-btn" onclick="doLogin()">
        <i style="margin-right:6px; font-style:normal;">🛡️</i>보안 시스템 접속
