          <div class="sub">서구 통합 성과 지표 · 실시간</div>
          <div class="score">92<span>점</span></div>
          <div class="trend"><i style="color:#34d399; font-style:normal;">⬆️</i> 전월 대비 4.2% 상승</div>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-title"><i style="font-style:normal;">🧠</i>AI 성공 가능성 예측 현황 <span style="font-size:10px;color:#9ca3af;font-weight:400;margin-left:auto">117 모듈</span></div>
          <div class="hscroll">
            <div class="h-card" onclick="toast('AI탭에서 상세 진단 결과를 확인하세요')">
              <div style="font-size:11px;font-weight:700;color:#374151;margin-bottom:6px">동그라미 상점가</div>
              <div style="font-size:26px;font-weight:800;color:#7c3aed">87%</div>
              <div class="prog-wrap" style="margin:6px 0"><div class="prog-bar" style="width:87%"></div></div>
              <span class="badge green">우수</span>
            </div>
            <div class="h-card" onclick="toast('AI탭에서 상세 진단 결과를 확인하세요')">
              <div style="font-size:11px;font-weight:700;color:#374151;margin-bottom:6px">세모세모 카페거리</div>
              <div style="font-size:26px;font-weight:800;color:#f97316">63%</div>
              <div class="prog-wrap" style="margin:6px 0"><div class="prog-bar orange" style="width:63%"></div></div>
              <span class="badge orange">처방 필요</span>
            </div>
            <div class="h-card" onclick="toast('AI탭에서 상세 진단 결과를 확인하세요')">
              <div style="font-size:11px;font-weight:700;color:#374151;margin-bottom:6px">별빛 전통시장</div>
              <div style="font-size:26px;font-weight:800;color:#ef4444">41%</div>
              <div class="prog-wrap" style="margin:6px 0"><div class="prog-bar red" style="width:41%"></div></div>
              <span class="badge red">취약</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-title"><i style="font-style:normal;">📡</i>기지국 유동인구 밀집도 <span style="font-size:10px;color:#9ca3af;font-weight:400;margin-left:auto">160·161 모듈</span></div>
          <canvas id="popChart" height="130"></canvas>
          <div style="margin-top:10px;display:flex;gap:16px">
            <div style="font-size:11px;color:#6b7280">🕐 피크타임: <b style="color:#7c3aed">13:00~15:00</b></div>
            <div style="font-size:11px;color:#6b7280">⏱ 평균 체류: <b style="color:#7c3aed">42분</b></div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-title"><i style="font-style:normal;">🕒</i>누적 인센티브 정산 기록 <span style="font-size:10px;color:#9ca3af;font-weight:400;margin-left:auto">총 128건</span></div>
          <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:8px">
            <div class="data-row" onclick="toast('상세 정산 내역을 불러옵니다.')" style="cursor:pointer">
              <div><div style="font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:#1f2937">온누리 페이백 15% 승인</div><div style="font-size:10px;color:#9ca3af">2026.06.18 · 동그라미 상점가</div></div>
              <span class="badge green">완료</span>
            </div>
            <div class="data-row" onclick="toast('상세 정산 내역을 불러옵니다.')" style="cursor:pointer">
              <div><div style="font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:#1f2937">중기부 공모 가점 +5점</div><div style="font-size:10px;color:#9ca3af">2026.06.15 · 별빛거리</div></div>
              <span class="badge purple">적용</span>
            </div>
            <div class="data-row" onclick="toast('상세 정산 내역을 불러옵니다.')" style="cursor:pointer">
              <div><div style="font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:#1f2937">지자체 매칭 예산 2,000만</div><div style="font-size:10px;color:#9ca3af">2026.06.10 · 세모상인회</div></div>
              <span class="badge green">완료</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div id="tab-platform" class="view-section">

        <div style="background:#fff;padding:12px 16px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;border-bottom:1px solid #f3f0ff;position:sticky;top:0;z-index:20">
          <span id="platform-title" style="font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:#374151">공공 전용 영상 DB (보안)</span>
          <label class="toggle-wrap">
            <input type="checkbox" id="platform-toggle" checked onchange="togglePlatform()">
            <span class="toggle-slider"></span>
          </label>
        </div>

        <div id="public-view">
          <div style="font-size:11px;color:#9ca3af;font-weight:700;padding:10px 14px 4px">총 842건 · 무결성 검증 완료</div>

          <div class="card" onclick="openBS()" style="cursor:pointer">
            <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px">
              <i style="font-size:28px;color:#8b5cf6; font-style:normal;">🎬</i>
              <div style="flex:1">
                <div style="font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:#1f2937">vid_report_260618.mp4</div>
                <div style="font-size:10px;color:#9ca3af">세모세모 카페 · 15MB</div>
              </div>
              <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:flex-end;gap:4px">
                <span class="badge red">AI 분류: 보안</span>
                <i style="color:#ef4444;font-size:14px; font-style:normal;">🔒</i>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

